0.1.0.name: connect20/Magedebugger
0.1.0.description: Our developers sometimes fell crazy when debug on customer live store. It's very hard to debug in silence. Now our Mage Debugger extension is a real magic. You can debug and see the result in your own screen, not the screen of store.
